        public java.util.Locale defaultOutputLocale
        Changing the locale changes the culture used in output e.g. for csv delimiters etc. Currently supports German and English. At some point this could be made dynamic based on culture info sent from client. Since all the development machines are German then it has just been parameterized here for now.
